Class Smell.CodeFragment

java.lang.Object
com.CodeSmell.smell.Smell.CodeFragment
Enclosing class:
Smell
public static class Smell.CodeFragment extends Object
Each detection is represented by a code fragment object containing the appropriate information needed to identify what the problem is in the CPG. Some (or for Project-level smells, all) of the fields may be left null
